Four persons have reportedly been shot after a fight broke out near an after-party for singer Justin Bieber. CNN reported that the Los Angeles Police Department said the shooting occurred at around 2:45am, after a fight broke out. It was learnt that a physical altercation between several people led to the shooting and gunshots were fired by a suspect who then fled the scene. Two of the victims who were shot were taken to nearby hospitals by paramedics while the other two self-transported to hospitals. The Police noted that the incident was not gang-related,‚Äù All four victims are in stable condition and no arrests have been made yet, according to the police.